body_html: Node and node-java bridging isn't officially supported by the TF team. Try asking a question on Stack Overflow, which is better suited for problems that are not bugs or feature requests. If you can track this back to a problem isolated within the Java API, please file another issue. Thanks!

body: Node and node-java bridging isn't officially supported by the TF team. Try asking a question on [Stack Overflow](stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/tensorflow), which is better suited for problems that are not bugs or feature requests. If you can track this back to a problem isolated within the Java API, please file another issue. Thanks!
